00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:19.120
with

74
00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:23.840
activated B-cell-like diffuse large B-cell lymphoma has worse outcomes.

75
00:04:24.300 --> 00:04:27.360
And that's been translated clinically into the use of

76
