00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:45.080
II clinical trial and then had a confirmatory Phase III trial that turned out

96
00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:49.100
to be a negative trial. And so while we

97
00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:53.100
were able to molecularly classify diffuse large B-cell lymphoma, we struggled with

98
00:05:53.140 --> 00:05:55.980
translating that into clinical applications that were

99
00:05:56.060 --> 00:05:59.892
useful.One of the things that we were able to do with these data and others,

