00:05:59.952 --> 00:06:03.512
though, was actually leverage them to be able to redefine the surrogate

101
00:06:03.612 --> 00:06:05.632
endpoints for diffuse large B-cell lymphoma.

102
00:06:05.662 --> 00:06:09.472
And this is work that I did with Tian Xu who

103
00:06:09.992 --> 00:06:10.452
is a

104
00:06:12.232 --> 00:06:16.012
biostatistician from Mayo Clinic, and investigators from

105
00:06:16.072 --> 00:06:19.832
across the world to be able to define a new surrogate endpoint

106
00:06:19.892 --> 00:06:23.692
for overall survival in diffuse large B-cell lymphoma progression,

107
00:06:24.072 --> 00:06:27.612
free survival, and that ultimately was used in a series of clinical

108
00:06:27.712 --> 00:06:30.492
trials that you'll see going forward.

109
00:06:31.052 --> 00:06:34.992
And I think this proves as an important point for the ways that

110
00:06:35.032 --> 00:06:38.332
