00:08:52.612 --> 00:08:56.272
shown here in green again maintaining a very similar

148
00:08:56.592 --> 00:09:00.572
survival benefit and confirmed that hazard ratio of 0.73 that

149
00:09:00.612 --> 00:09:04.172
was seen at the initial

150
00:09:04.212 --> 00:09:08.052
evaluation. And so as we look towards the

151
00:09:08.092 --> 00:09:11.892
future, the question is what is really next for patients with diffuse large

152
00:09:11.952 --> 00:09:14.632
B-cell lymphoma with that now established as a new

153
00:09:15.592 --> 00:09:17.432
