154
00:09:17.812 --> 00:09:21.692
And I think the next thing that we really are hoping for is the development

155
00:09:21.712 --> 00:09:25.372
of subtype differentiated therapy which has remained a

156
00:09:25.432 --> 00:09:28.872
challenge for patients. We do know in secondary analyses

157
00:09:29.272 --> 00:09:33.192
of the POLARIX trial shown here from data that

