00:09:33.212 --> 00:09:37.152
were first presented by Franck Morschhäuser in our group at the

159
00:09:37.212 --> 00:09:40.652
ASH meetings shown in terms of progression-free survivals and then

160
00:09:40.712 --> 00:09:44.572
eventually also published as hazard

