00:09:44.632 --> 00:09:48.612
ratios and forest plots in that JCO publication that

162
00:09:48.652 --> 00:09:52.452
the predominant benefit for patients with diffuse large B-cell lymphoma when

163
00:09:52.612 --> 00:09:56.432
stratified by genotype is in the group that had the

