174
00:10:31.062 --> 00:10:35.012
And so in my mind, if you want to use these data to inform therapy,

175
00:10:35.072 --> 00:10:38.612
and I'll show you some strategies potentially for doing that, it really needs to be

176
00:10:38.732 --> 00:10:42.112
based on gene expression profiling as the way that you define that.

177
00:10:43.412 --> 00:10:43.732
And so

178
00:10:44.592 --> 00:10:48.512
in the interim, there have been a number of things that have come up beyond just

179
00:10:48.592 --> 00:10:51.632
gene expression profiling to be able to define subtypes.

