00:14:04.366 --> 00:14:08.346
And so I think this is something that will help us to think about the ways

232
00:14:08.376 --> 00:14:12.296
that we use molecular classifiers in the future.

233
00:14:12.336 --> 00:14:15.876
The other thing that we're thinking about here is how do we ultimately get this to

